{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Make the following structural changes across two theme files:
    
    1. **Remove social icons from the Payment methods block (ai_gen_block_96b5033)**: Completely remove the social icons display, their settings (Instagram URL, Facebook URL, YouTube URL, TikTok URL, LinkedIn URL, icon size, icon spacing, show social icons toggle) from both the block schema and the rendered output. Keep all payment method functionality (PayPal, Visa, Mastercard, Amex) intact.
    
    2. **Add social icons into the LB Footer section (lb-footer)**: 
       - In the Shopify editor side panel: add the social icon fields (show social icons toggle, Instagram URL, Facebook URL, YouTube URL, TikTok URL, LinkedIn URL, icon size, icon spacing) so they appear directly beneath the "Location Text" field in the Brand Column settings group.
       - On the storefront: render the social icons visually inside the brand column, directly below where the Location Text ("Cape Town, Western Cape, South Africa") is displayed.
       - Pre-populate the social URLs with the existing values: Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/graffitistylewriter, Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kevinschiffer, YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/graffitistylewriter
       - Social icons must always display in full brand colour (never greyscale) in both light and dark theme modes.
       - The social icons should use the same icon style and sizing as they currently appear in the Payment methods block.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-payment-methods-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .ai-payment-methods-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: {{ block.settings.alignment }};
    gap: 16px;
    width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-payment-methods-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .ai-payment-icons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: {{ block.settings.icon_spacing }}px;
    justify-content: {{ block.settings.alignment }};
  }

  .ai-payment-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-payment-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-payment-methods-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-payment-methods-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-payment-methods-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.title != blank %}
      <h3 class="ai-payment-methods-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</h3>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-payment-icons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
